description:
 This check monitors the status of each temperature sensor.
 
 The service goes {WARN} or {CRIT}

 - in case of reaching a state which is not Normal
 
 - Reaching a treshhold


 Otherwise the service is {OK}.


discovery:
 One service is created per temperature sensor.

